import React from 'react'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import '../styles/AdminHome.css'; import AdminHeader from './AdminHeader'; import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'; import { faChartLine, faUserGraduate, faBookOpen, faMoneyBillWave } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'; const AdminHome = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const handleCreateCourse = () => { navigate('/addcourse'); }; const stats = [ { icon: faChartLine, title: 'Total Courses', value: '125', trend: '+12%' }, { icon: faUserGraduate, title: 'Active Students', value: '8,450', trend: '+8%' }, { icon: faBookOpen, title: 'Courses Created', value: '35', trend: '+5%' }, { icon: faMoneyBillWave, title: 'Revenue', value: '$45,800', trend: '+15%' } ]; const courseCategories = [ { id: 1, name: 'Programming', icon: 'fa-laptop-code', image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542744173-8e7e53415bb0?w=800&auto=format', count: '35', progress: '85' }, { id: 2, name: 'Data Science', icon: 'fa-database', image: 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQesynHzOBv4W3hwcjEdV6QPhoIzXfQK8-Aig&s', count: '28', progress: '70' }, { id: 3, name: 'Web Development', icon: 'fa-code', image: 'https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/web-development-coding-programming-internet-technology-business-concept-web-development-coding-programming-internet-technology-121903546.jpg', count: '22', progress: '65' }, { id: 4, name: 'AI & ML', icon: 'fa-robot', image: 'https://media.istockphoto.com/id/966248982/photo/robot-with-education-hud.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=9eoZYRXNZsuU3edU87PksxN4Us-c9rB6IR7U_IGZ-U8=', count: '18', progress: '55' }, { id: 5, name: 'Business', icon: 'fa-chart-line', image: 'https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/businessman-using-tablet-laptop-analyzing-sales-data-economic-growth-graph-chart-business-strategy-digital-marketing-154742021.jpg', count: '20', progress: '75' } ]; return ( <>
